---------------------  New user root role ------------------------

$ sudo useradd -ou 0 -g 0 john
$ sudo passwd john


---------------------  Current user root role ---------------------

$ grep john /etc/passwd
john:x:1001:1001::/home/alice:/bin/sh

$ grep john /etc/passwd
john:x:0:0::/home/john:/bin/sh

$ sudo usermod -a -G root john


adduser tom
usermod -aG sudo tom
visudo
tom ALL=(ALL:ALL) ALL
su - tom
grep '^sudo' /etc/group
